	(text "Indicator LEDs for High Voltage Lines 1 and 2. HV# ON signal comes from power board. \nOctocoupler helps isolate delicate circuitry from the potentially high voltage \ncoming in on the ON lines. Signal gets sent to MCU to indicate if line is on."
